ions dancing across the surface, subtle eyelash texture visible along the upper lids, and fine pores subtly textured across the skin; her complexion displays a natural warm blush on her cheeks, faint soya spots scattered delicately beneath both eyes, and a gentle, natural sheen from ambient sunlight; her short black bob haircut flows softly with a slight side-swept fringe catching the light, each strand individually rendered with realistic weight and movement; she wears a dark navy cropped t-shirt with a faded, slightly worn graphic on the back, paired with high-waisted distressed blue denim shorts exhibiting raw, frayed hems and a bright orange belt buckle that catches the light; her footwear consists of sturdy dark blue platform boots with thick tan soles and crisp white laces, subtly detailed with creases and wear; the lighting is soft natural sunlight filtering through urban haze, casting dramatic, elongated shadows across the gritty concrete surface, with a shallow depth of field blurring the background into an atmospheric alleyway of muted gray walls and a distant vertical pole, rendered in cinematic depth of field with creamy bokeh and atmospheric perspective to emphasize the subject’s presence — every texture is ultra-realistic: the fine grain of the concrete, the subtle sheen of her skin, the frayed stitching on her shorts, the worn leather of her boots, all captured with precision, emotion, and hyper-detailed realism., small beauty moles under both eyes,, Ethnicity: Japanese beauty, Authentic Japanese features\n\nSkin: Detailed skin texture, Subtle imperfections, Soft natural makeup\n\nAtmosphere: Soft cinematic lighting, Hyper-realistic, Shot on Sony A7R IV"]},{"id":119,"type":"PreviewImage","pos":[777.5927483235677,-322.8232174149779],"size":[322.95389668090843,306.87293417022715],"flags":{},"order":6,"mode":0,"inputs":[{"localized_name":"画像","name":"images","type":"IMAGE","link":195}],"outputs":[],"properties":{"cnr_id":"comfy-core","ver":"0.12.3","Node